      • getStroldDatNewWords

        public java.lang.String getStroldDatNewWords()
        Get Level date as String for Label If the date is 01.01.2000, return empty String, because there is no word in level. For the oldDate: if nr of the level is 0, return empty String, because there is no word in level.
        Returns:
        the date of the oldest word in the New Word level as String
